<section class=" container" id="aboutOffice">
    
    <div class="row">
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <div class="container">
                <h2 class="about_office">About the Office</h2>
                    <p class="about_office_text">
                        Join a team of people who are mutually passionate about pushing the limits and breaking records. If you think you've got what it takes to join our global award-winning team, to be part of place that looks to create value and challenge the status quo, a place to work and learn from the best. And if for you this digital world is a career, you belong with us!
